description:
Enviably positioned in Harrington Grove's prestigious Dianella precinct, every inch of this home exudes luxury and epitomises what it means to reside in the Harrington Grove estate.

With exceptional design features, over 970sqm of land and a layout that allows for privacy within the family as well as
multiple communal family areas, 74 Cameron Circuit takes executive living to another level.

Highlight Features:

- Five bedrooms and four bathrooms (two ensuites)
- Oversized double garage with dual side access for vehicles, boat etc
- Ducted air-conditioning
- Media room + additional three living areas
- Masterchef's kitchen with oversized Island Bench
- Two balconies
- Pool, built-in spa and separate free standing spa
- 10kw, 25 solar panel system
- 60mm stone, waterfall edge kitchen bench top
- Entertainers paradise featuring alfresco area as well as lounge area adjacent to the pool
- Large storage shed
- Neatly landscaped gardens

Lifestyle Features:

- Harrington Park Plaza – 2.6km
- Harrington Park Public School – 2km
- St Benedict's Catholic College – 200m
- Harrington Grove Country Club (provides access to gym, pool, tennis & basketball court
facilities) – 1.2km
- Gregory Hills Town Centre – 2.8km

An executive, Harrington Grove residence awaits and opportunities like this are not to be missed. For
any further enquiries or to arrange your inspection, contact the Century 21 Pereira
Group Team on 4647 9727.

*Century 21 Pereira Group believes all information contained herein is accurate at the time of
advertising. However, we encourage interested parties to conduct their own enquiries.

******** COVID-19 Statement for all inspecting parties ********

conducted by Century 21 Pereira Group, whether they be Sales Open Homes or Rental Open Homes
